name: "Bill Gates" circa 2016
description: Referred to as the "King of Software", entrepreneur Bill Gates founded the world's largest software company, Microsoft, subsequently becoming one of the richest men in the world. Gates developed an early interest in computer science and by age 12 Gates was involved with various computer programming projects throughout his school. In addition to his work at Microsoft, Gates is known for founding the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation, one of the largest charitable foundations in the world.
